<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka thagau Ni, Nang, Hukdampa,
 Nang na naih tieng thimna a bei;
 Na nasemte apat na mel,
 Lieh di'n thepna mei zin phal ki'n.

[V2]
 2. Zan dai kiek ka ihmut laiin,
 Ipmu a ka mit ka sin tieng;
 Na anga kumsawt a chawl ding,
 Nawp ding zie ka ngaihtuoh hi hen.

[V3]
 3. Nitum in Nang ei umpih in,
 Nang tello in ka hing thei puoi;
 Zan a naih tieng ei umpih in,
 Nang tel loin thih ka ngam puoi.

[V4]
 4. Na cha vakvai mi khenkhat te'n,
 Tuni'n na Aw ngailo mahleu;
 Lalpa, lungsietna nasem in,
 Gitloh mun ah umsak ta ki'n.

[V5]
 5. Ka thawh tieng u leh hung naiin,
 Khawvel khela ka len mauin;
 Na hehpih tuipi a luta,
 Hin thaka Van ka tun chan un.</lyrics>
<title>SUN OF MY SOUL</title>
<hymn_number>195</hymn_number>
</song>